Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H002D2D2D\bord2\3c&H00EFEFEF\fs40\fn微软雅黑\b1\frz16.47\pos(273.6,553)}動畫研廢部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz4.794\b1\c&H00644FC7\bord2\fs40\3c&H00FFFFFF\pos(513.6,202.6)}絕不原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz5.42\pos(504,65)\bord0\c&H00C7424A\b1}蠻橫的{\c&H006A645E}校長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz346.2\c&H005234C1\bord0\b1\fn微软雅黑\pos(905.6,162.6)}請求!
